tomllib.md
     1â†’# `tomllib` â€“ Tomli in the standard library
     2â†’
     3â†’Tomli was added to the Python standard library in Python 3.11.
    13â†’## Converting Tomli to tomllib
    14â†’
    15â†’### Sync status
    16â†’
    17â†’`tomllib` in CPython commit https://github.com/python/cpython/commit/deaf509e8fc6e0363bd6f26d52ad42f976ec42f2
    18â†’matches Tomli commit https://github.com/hukkin/tomli/commit/7e563eed5286b5d46b8290a9f56a86d955b23a9a
    19â†’
    20â†’### Steps to convert
    21â†’
    22â†’- Move everything in `tomli:src/tomli` to `cpython:Lib/tomllib`. Exclude `py.typed`.
